  "description": "A solitary figure stands on a dark, sandy beach facing a turbulent ocean under a dramatic, cloud-filled sky. The sky is a blend of deep blues, purples, and faint pinks and oranges, suggesting either sunrise or sunset. Waves crash onto the shore, illuminated by the faint light filtering through the clouds. The figure is silhouetted against the bright horizon, appearing small and contemplative against the vastness of the sea and sky. The beach is dark and wet, reflecting some of the sky's colors. The overall impression is one of solitude, power, and the beauty of nature.",
